kies we planned planted and cultivated a firstofitskind sustainable garden outside gate a of the ballpark we then took the freshly harvested herbs and vegetables and used them in recipes and salad stations at the ballpark’s restaurant see the impact of this innovation impact the garden was a hit our team at coors field was not only building a more sustainable community and future but also providing fans and guests fresher menu options than they would get at a typical stadium going forward we’ll look to continually innovate and improve our food services at all the stadiums and arenas we serve contact us in a national poll by turnkey sports we were voted the top food service provider in the sports and entertainment space find out more about sports and entertainment explore our services our sports and entertainment team has a lot more to bring to your venue facilities services retail merchandise latest news lsu announces partnership with aramark as new campus athletics concessionaire june    we are honored to partner with one of the most prestigious athletic departments in all of college sports lsu has some of the most energetic and passionate fans and we look forward to utilizing our insights and expertise to deliver a dynamic food and beverage program that enhances the game day experience as the  nba and nhl playoff races heat up aramark rolls out new menus for conference finals aramark opens baseball season with new roster of mouthwatering menus from the gridiron to the grill football hall of famer eric dickerson teams up with aramark for new  view all news how can we help let’s give your fans the food service experience they want contact us contact us select about aramark aramark nyse armk is in the customer service business across food facilities and uniforms wherever people work learn recover and play united by a passion to serve our  team members deliver experiences that enrich and nourish the lives of millions of people in  countries around the world every day 